Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手前想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 才会反被我利用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要中这种非常明显的陷阱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说 我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是看你不懂才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的一举一动 真是漏洞百出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于让我找到破绽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你这个家伙太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的手里剑暴露了我的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是故意露出破绽的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 我怎么会上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道已经被老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助绝不会发生那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 小心后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫做“沉着冷静地判断”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会再中老师设下的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不及格 卡卡西的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 刚才怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在才察觉 似乎太晚了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音…是小樱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者战术的心得之二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱那家伙 很简单就上当了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻术…幻觉催眠术的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪那家伙会轻易上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟那些家伙不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是等你抢到铃铛之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样直接冲过来是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子真不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可没空看《亲热天堂》了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助刚才满身是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 不要抛下我先去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来圆柱后面是那个样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来便当就放在石头上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认 你跟他两的确不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 下忍居然会这种忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的查克拉应该还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土遁.心中斩首术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者战术心得之三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 不能动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就能崭露头角了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做打压新秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便没有傻乎乎地去抢铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要躲在这里把便当吃掉 我也就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他之间居然差这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是死人头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你平安无事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间紧张 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你还想继续抢铃铛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定能得手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你果然是很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师那么厉害 我绝对抢不到铃铛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我就不能和佐助在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正时间也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就不要逞强了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上 只有我才能杀得了那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…我哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一个复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要超越那个家伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没空在这里跟你耗着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要亲手宰了那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个肚子都饿得呱呱叫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 关于这次的演习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你们也没有必要回忍者学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我刚刚只是昏倒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也能算及格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情胜利了 真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就表示 我们三个人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你们三个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不必再当忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止 还没有一个学生及格过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让那些孩子们去当忍者是不是正确
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 卡卡西的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不用当忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确没有抢到铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可也没必要让我们放弃做忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个都是没有资格做忍者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会说你是小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把你的脚踩在佐助的头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们几个 是不是瞧不起忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为为什么要分组进行这个演习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个完全没有搞懂这个测验的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判断你们是否能通过这个测验的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以从刚才起 我就想问这个问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们脑袋里装的是不是浆糊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们懂不懂三人一组的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一组又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是团队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们互相帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 不过现在才知道已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以抢到铃铛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是铃铛只有两个 要怎么团队合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人拼命抢铃铛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人一定要忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么团队合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会起内讧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们故意安排成会起内讧的测验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个考试的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要选拔出在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能不顾自己的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先执行团队合作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是看看你们自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不把鸣人放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满脑子只有不知身在何处的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是一个人横冲直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你则把他们两个当成了绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去单打独斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务是以小组来执行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对忍者来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卓越的个人技术的确不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 团队合作却比这个更为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂团队合作的独行侠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让同伴陷入危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还会送命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举个例子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 把鸣人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然佐助就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴被挟持为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼迫你做出痛苦的抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而同伴的性命也会因此难保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所执行的任务 都是玩命的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无数姓名刻在这石头上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全都是被村民称为英雄的忍者们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个 就是这个 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定也要把名字刻上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄 英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能这么轻易地挂掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这不是普通的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么样的英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说嘛 快说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是殉职的英雄们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殉职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了执行任务而身亡的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是慰灵碑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好几个朋友的名字刻在这石碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再给你们最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 下午之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢铃铛的战斗会变得更加激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有想挑战的人才能吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是决不许给鸣人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他不守规矩 想吃独食的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人敢分给他吃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就淘汰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 我就是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 伊鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不要恨卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算没吃饭 也不会怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我没有任何影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才老师不是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他现在也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午我们三人一起去抢铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你碍手碍脚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢了 赶快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在减肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 因为我吃得比佐助少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得他什么时候出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗 你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的胆子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢违抗我订的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因…因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…因为…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 不是你自己说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是三人小组对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个人一条心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 就是啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一条心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个是第一批
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的小鬼们只会乖乖听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破忍者世界的规则和铁律的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都叫他废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂得重视同伴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更差劲的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演习到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7班从明天起开始执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我成为忍者咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快帮我解开绳子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都是这种不入流的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为有像样一点的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果居然是护送这种老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我们是小鬼就瞧不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会借此机会好好表现的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老头子 你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将来可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要任务 向波之国出发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你 我还会继续表现的哦
